 generic [ref=e193]: Posts\n            - button \"Search\" [ref=e197] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - generic [ref=e200]:\n                - img\n      - generic [ref=e207]:\n        - generic [ref=e210]:\n          - generic \"YouTube Video Player\" [ref=e214]:\n            - generic [ref=e217]:\n              - generic [ref=e219]: My great-grandfather was a real peaky\n              - generic [ref=e221]: blinder. He's criminalized\n            - generic [ref=e222]:\n              - generic [ref=e223] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - slider \"Seek slider\" [ref=e224]\n                - generic:\n                  - generic:\n                    - generic:\n                      - slider \"Click or scroll the panel for the precise seeking.\"\n              - generic [ref=e235]:\n                - generic [ref=e236]:\n                  - button \"Pause (k)\" [ref=e237] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img\n                  - generic [ref=e238]:\n                    - button \"Unmute (m)\" [ref=e240] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img\n                    - slider \"Volume\"\n                  - button \"0 Minutes 2 Seconds of 41 Minutes 26 Seconds\" [ref=e244] [cursor=pointer]: 0:02 / 41:26\n                - generic [ref=e246]:\n                  - button [ref=e247] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img\n                  - button \"Settings\" [ref=e248] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img\n          - generic [ref=e249]:\n            - generic [ref=e250]:\n              - 'heading \"The Real Peaky Blinders: What Do We Actually Know? 41 minutes\" [level=3] [ref=e251]':\n                - 'link \"The Real Peaky Blinders: What Do We Actually Know?\" [ref=e252] [cursor=pointer]':\n                  - /url: /watch?v=jVDIHkisF54\n              - generic [ref=e255]:\n                - generic [ref=e256]: 104,905 views\n                - generic [ref=e257]: •2 weeks ago\n            - generic [ref=e258]:\n              - generic [ref=e260]:\n                - text: \"The Real Peaky Blinders: What Do We Actually Know? Join historians Luke Tomes and Carl Chinn MBE as they explore the real history behind the infamous gang at the Black Country Living Museum, the filming location for the hit TV series (a Caryn Mandabach and Tiger Aspect Production – created and written by Steven Knight) With decades of research into the thugs, gangs and violence in Birmingham through the late 19th and early 20th century, Carl helps to sort the fact from the fiction, identifying the real-life figures behind some of the iconic characters, including Tommy Shelby, Alfie Solomons and Billy Kimber. Carl also makes a shocking revelation about his own personal connection to the gang, his great-grandfather having once been a member of the outfit. ‘Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man’ is out in select cinemas from 6th March 2026, and will be streaming globally on Netflix from 20th March 2026. Want to find out more about the real Peaky Blinders? Check out Carl’s book series on the subject and make sure to visit the Black Country Living Museum:\"\n                - link \"https://bclm.com/\" [ref=e261] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description&redir_token=QUFFLUhqbnQtekpySEdqOUc0OF9ISWw3T0EtTEFrRm5Zd3xBQ3Jtc0tsUVl3UXk1dUc3ZHRzZmJEc0hET3laMmx6RHJzc3kwLUhZQ0VYT2c3b2RpMUdOUVc4RG9hYVI5VElUWTVSU0pxVUFKWmlTUmJaRUIwbFlZTVJTNEFuVGNINEhVdFYtNmFGNEdCd0VWWVdzSUZDU2o2Yw&q=https%3A%2F%2Fbclm.com%2F\n                - text: \"Photo credits: The West Midlands Police Museum / BirminghamLives You can now become a History Hit member right here on YouTube! Join for access to a new exclusive documentary every week, and access to over 160+ of our documentaries presented by world-renowned historians like Dan Snow, Eleanor Janega, Tristan Hughes, Mary Beard, Matt Lewis and more. Get an exclusive release every week by signing up here:\"\n                - link \"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZwU...\" [ref=e262] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZwU2G-KVl-P-O-B35chZOQ/join\n                - link \"#peakyblinders\" [ref=e263] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /hashtag/peakyblinders\n                - link \"#netflix\" [ref=e264] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /hashtag/netflix\n                - link \"#realhistory\" [ref=e265] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /hashtag/realhistory\n                - text: 00:00 Intro 01:03 Did the Peaky Blinders Exist? 03:08 Where Did the Name Come From? 04:30 Peaky Blinders Fashion (Flat Cap Razor Blades) 06:03 Photographs of First Peaky Blinders 07:49 Slums of 19th Century Birmingham 09:14 Back-to-Back Housing 13:15 Inside a Victorian Back-to-Back House 16:05 Birmingham's Industrial Rise 17:25 Emergence of First Gangs 19:53 Violence in the Streets 24:16 Carl's Great-Grandfather (Peaky Blinder) 25:48 Real Life Characters (Billy Kimber, Alfie Solomons) 29:10 The Real 'Tommy Shelby' 32:20 Police Crackdown 37:16 Fall and Legacy of the Peaky Blinders 39:55 'Peaky Blinders' TV Show\n              - button \"Read more\" [ref=e266] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - link \"Read more\" [ref=e268]:\n                  - /url: /watch?v=jVDIHkisF54\n        - generic [ref=e272]:\n          - heading \"For You\" [level=2] [ref=e275]:\n            - generic [ref=e277]: For You\n          - generic [ref=e279]:\n            - generic [ref=e282]:\n              - generic [ref=e284]:\n                - link [ref=e286] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /watch?v=0btAQ7jcRPI&pp=0gcJCcMKAYcqIYzv\n                  - img [ref=e288]\n                  - img [ref=e291]:\n                    - generic [ref=e292]: 3:20:22\n                  - generic:\n                    - generic: Now playing\n                    - generic:\n                      - img\n                - generic [ref=e293] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - generic [ref=e295]