{"type":"message","id":"646f1129","parentId":"68345676","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:27:06.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"TimelineChannel only has 2 Shorts visible. Let me now move on to other channels. Let me get transcripts for TimelineChannel's Shorts and then check other channels. Let me be more efficient and batch the transcript extraction.\n\nI have the following Shorts to extract transcripts from:\n- TimelineChannel:\n  - zvVhCb8XiCE - \"Leaving Neverland II: Surviving Michael Jackson | Official Trailer | Exclusively on @RealStories\" - 20K views\n  - hy-TGbLYm7g - \"The deadly influenza pandemic of 1918 💀… #shorts\" - 27K views\n\nLet me extract transcripts in batch and move to the next channels. \n\nI'll speed this up by pulling transcripts from all the remaining channels at once rather than doing them one by one.","thinkingSignature":"0ba27848660deec0860a7bf6bf23d46a7b07f49b0ef43de2be8da84b63c72ae5"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me extract transcripts for the channels I've found so far, and check remaining channels.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v77age0jkrrx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/zvVhCb8XiCE\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1 && echo \"---NEXT---\" && summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/hy-TGbLYm7g\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1","yieldMs":60000,"timeout":90}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v77age0jkrrx_2","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"807C31555A855924C511E400A3AF2BF0","url":"https://www.youtube.com/@TheInformationArchive/shorts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47242,"output":363,"cacheRead":16095,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63700,"cost":{"input":0.014172599999999999,"output":0.00043559999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0009656999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015573899999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774312018876,"re