{"type":"message","id":"a2809199","parentId":"646f1129","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:27:13.697Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v77age0jkrrx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Transcript:\nWhat they're alleging is\nthat Michael Jackson was a pedophile.\nThat's not negligence.\nPursuing this was\nthe act of fighting back.\nPeople must have known.\nI can't imagine how they didn't know.\nThere was knowledge\nthat there was something weird going on,\nand nobody in the organization\ndid anything about it.\nI want my day in court.\nI don't buy it.\nI think these two\nare financially motivated,\nand I think you are.\nMichael Jackson got away with this\nfor a long time.\nIf the corporation facilitates\nabuse of children,\nthen the corporation\nshould be held liable.\nPeriod.\nA California jury in a box.\nThat's their fear.\nPedophiles don't operate in a vacuum.\nJudgment is entered for the defendants.\nThis fight’s long from over.\nThis is not right.\nIt's draining to go through this\nover and over again.\nThey seek delay.\nWe seek justice.\nWhen it comes,\nI'll be ready.\n\n3.2s · 1m 8s YouTube · 150 words · text via transcript/captionTracks\n---NEXT---\nTranscript:\nin three days it has affected seventy\npercent of the population day after day\nthey set sail from New York Boston and\nPhiladelphia\nto transport such numbers\nthe number of transports and routes\nmultiplies\nsoon ship's dock simultaneously\nLiverpool Brest Bordeaux and even\nMarseille during the eight-day crossing\nplatoons of contact cases become\nbattalions of flu victims\n[Music]\nSpain is the first to break the news of\nthe illness\nand trees neutral and its newspapers are\nfree to inform the world the illness\nwill henceforth be called the Spanish\nFlu\n\n3.0s · 49s YouTube · 90 words · text via transcript/captionTracks"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7180,"aggregated":"Transcript:\nWhat they're alleging is\nthat Michael Jackson was a pedophile.\nThat's not negligence.\nPursuing this was\nthe act of fighting back.\nPeople must have known.\nI can't imagine how they didn't know.\nThere was knowledge\nthat there was something weird going on,\nand nobody in the organization\ndid anything about it.\nI want my day in court.\nI don't buy it.\nI think these two\nare financially motivated,\nand I think you are.\nMichael Jackson got away with this\nfor a long time.\nIf the corporation facilitates\nabuse of children,\nthen the corporation\nshould be held liable.\nPeriod.\nA California jury in a box.\nThat's their fear.\nPedophiles don't operate in a vacuum.\nJudgment is entered for the defendants.\nThis fight’s long from over.\nThis is not right.\nIt's draining to go through this\nover and over again.\nThey seek delay.\nWe seek justice.\nWhen it comes,\nI'll be ready.\n\n3.2s · 1m 8s YouTube · 150 words · text via transcript/captionTracks\n---NEXT---\nTranscript:\nin three days it has affected seventy\npercent of the population day after day\nthey set sail from New York Boston and\nPhiladelphia\nto transport such numbers\nthe number of transports and routes\nmultiplies\nsoon ship's dock simultaneously\nLiverpool Brest Bordeaux and even\nMarseille during the eight-day crossing\nplatoons of contact cases become\nbattalions of flu victims\n[Music]\nSpain is the first to break the news of\nthe illness\nand trees neutral and its newspapers are\nfree to inform the world the illness\nwill henceforth be called the Spanish\nFlu\n\n3.0s · 49s YouTube · 90 words · text via transcript/captionTracks","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-yoyos"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774312033695}}
