flower\" [ref=e200]':\n              - /url: /shorts/rEC7-9u8gnU\n            - generic [ref=e201]: 632 views\n          - button \"More actions\" [ref=e203] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e207]:\n              - img\n        - generic [ref=e214]:\n          - link [ref=e215] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /shorts/paaCGkCu1zA\n          - generic [ref=e219] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - 'link \"How the Pilgrims Paid For Their Colony #history #ushistory #discoverpilgrim #map #plymouth\" [ref=e220]':\n              - /url: /shorts/paaCGkCu1zA\n            - generic [ref=e221]: 1.4K views\n          - button \"More actions\" [ref=e223] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e227]:\n              - img\n        - generic [ref=e234]:\n          - link [ref=e235] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /shorts/J136uxJu9t8\n          - generic [ref=e239] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - 'link \"Pilgrims Were NOT Puritans! #history #ushistory #pilgrim #thanksgiving #mayflower\" [ref=e240]':\n              - /url: /shorts/J136uxJu9t8\n            - generic [ref=e241]: 7.9K views\n          - button \"More actions\" [ref=e243] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e247]:\n              - img\n        - generic [ref=e254]:\n          - link [ref=e255] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /shorts/qEddWylyizU\n          - generic [ref=e259] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - 'link \"How 14 Men Began Massachusetts #history #ushistory #map #massachusetts #puritan #salem\" [ref=e260]':\n              - /url: /shorts/qEddWylyizU\n            - generic [ref=e261]: 13K views\n          - button \"More actions\" [ref=e263] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e267]:\n              - img\n        - generic [ref=e274]:\n          - link [ref=e275] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /shorts/_EA6Gq49L9A\n          - generic [ref=e279] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - 'link \"Founding of Salem, Dorchester Company #history #massachusetts #