{"type":"message","id":"03c1778b","parentId":"54a5e16c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:29:00.388Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"AI HISTORY has many Shorts! Let me extract transcripts from a few of the top ones. Let me pick 5-7:\n\n1. yLcX33-punA - \"The Real Story of Vasco da Gama's Sea Route Discovery\" - 7.3K views\n2. 4osByhu2Nj0 - \"People Were Getting Sick… Until This Ancient Water Trick Was Found\" - 22K views\n3. LGVja7oEjGQ - \"Something Strange Happened to This Dough Overnight\" - 420K views\n4. pAgMtmZPW6I - \"He Was Saving Food… But Made Something New 🍯\" - 242K views\n\n\n5. yUe0knrKwGA - \"He Accidentally Made Something That Changed Everything\" - 257K views\n6. a0fMTaxnuXw - \"He Boiled Fruit Peels… The Smell Stopped Everyone\" - 2.7M views\n\nNow I'll pull transcripts from all six of these.","thinkingSignature":"4733225a5ddfc28101efbcca082cb57b351a3032ea75513cc103f265c1587403"},{"type":"text","text":"AI HISTORY has many Shorts. Let me extract transcripts from key ones.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xs9p8p22hws2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/yLcX33-punA\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1 && echo \"---NEXT---\" && summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/4osByhu2Nj0\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1 && echo \"---NEXT---\" && summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/LGVja7oEjGQ\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1 && echo \"---NEXT---\" && summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/pAgMtmZPW6I\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1 && echo \"---NEXT---\" && summarize \"https://youtube.com/shorts/a0fMTaxnuXw\" --youtube auto --extract-only 2>&1","yieldMs":120000,"timeout":150}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":73768,"output":447,"cacheRead":16095,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90310,"cost":{"input":0.022130399999999998,"output":0.0005364,"cacheRead":0.0009656999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0236